Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, in a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:27.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gazin' up to the Promised Land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:31.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:33.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.75,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake！ Up！ Your！ Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave and boiling heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を示せ High！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Boost！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:29.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real deal！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more liars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:31.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition's ON, my heart is on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fire Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:27.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:31.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:33.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:44.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:16.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:18.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:20.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:29.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:31.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:35.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…and so, we met in the deep dark and shattered place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:42.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one will come to us. They left us here with disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:48.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all abanded sadness. We all abanded kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of hatred. There's no hope, then take this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘で建った塔の　深層で燃える炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（早々気を付けろ背後） 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:03.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready. Burn up！ Liars！ In this cold night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:06.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただで消え去る罪など無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:10.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby, cry out louder to this bad luck
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,God, hear the scream, share us your light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:22.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, now stand up and head up cause we're falling up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（Who is the bloody liar？ You all the bloody liar）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創傷疼いている　何故痛いくらい 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:32.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah 今疼き出す…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:39.63,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's behind the truth. We know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:47.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's behind the truth. We know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:35.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们相遇在这个深幽破碎之境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:42.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会来 他们把我们留在这蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是孤独的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:48.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀遗弃了我们 仁慈遗弃了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界充满着憎恶 没有希望 执此前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用谎言树立的塔 在其深处燃烧的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（随时小心身后）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.09,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:03.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准备 燃烧吧骗子！在这冰冷的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:06.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪必须付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:10.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 宝贝 为你的厄运大声哭喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 请聆听这哭号 赐下您的圣光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:22.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜 匍匐跌倒之人请起身抬头吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（谁是可恶的骗子？你们全是可恶的骗子）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创伤在隐隐作痛 为何如此痛彻心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:32.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 此刻疼痛再起...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:39.63,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:47.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
